data.description: Beautiful 2 story home located in Hawks Nest Subdivision. Master suite with patio located on the first floor. This residential home offers a spacious open floor plan with a breakfast nook, radiant kitchen, a gas fireplace located in the living room on the first floor. On the upper levels we have an additional family room, 3 bedrooms, linen closet, and a full bath with 2 vanities. This home also has an incredible backyard with great RV parking and a privacy fence with a 10 ft double RV access gate!
